OL,3,CSouthern Water apologises after 'one
OL,4,Cof worst pollution spills' at Camber
OL,5,CSands
OL,7,FSouthern Water has apologised after
OL,8,Fwhat's believed to be millions of
OL,9,Fplastic pellets washed up on beaches
OL,10,Fin East Sussex, including Camber Sands.
OL,12,FLocal environmental groups and
OL,13,Fvolunteers have been working alongside
OL,14,Fthe Environment Agency and Rother
OL,15,FDistrict Council to clear up the
OL,16,Fspillage as best they can.
OL,18,FThe pellets which are known as 'bio-
OL,19,Fbeads' are commonly used by water
OL,20,Ftreatment plants as part of the
OL,21,Fcleaning process.
