OL,5,CSands
OL,7,FEnvironmental charities say it's one
OL,8,Fof the worst incidents they have ever
OL,9,Fseen, and warned the pellets were
OL,10,Fcatastrophic for marine life.
OL,12,FIt's reported that a higher than usual
OL,13,Fnumber of dead seals and harbour
OL,14,Fporpoises had been washing up onto the
OL,15,Fbeach last week.
