OL,3,CSouthern Water apologises after 'one
OL,4,Cof worst pollution spills' at Camber
OL,5,CSands
OL,7,FA spokesman for Southern Water said:
OL,8,F"After completing the initial stages
OL,9,Fof a thorough investigation, which is
OL,10,Fcontinuing, we believe it is highly
OL,11,Flikely that the beads have come from
OL,12,Four Eastbourne Wastewater Treatment
OL,13,FWorks.
OL,15,F"We've identified a failure of a
OL,16,Fscreening filter which has apparently
OL,17,Fled to beads used in the treatment
OL,18,Fprocess being released into the sea
OL,19,Fduring heavy rainfall.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
