OL,3,CSouthern Water apologises after 'one
OL,4,Cof worst pollution spills' at Camber
OL,5,CSands
OL,7,F"The screen should have prevented this
OL,8,Foccurring.
OL,10,F"We are very sorry this has happened
OL,11,Fand are doing everything possible to
OL,12,Finvestigate and resolve the problem.
OL,14,F'We'll provide further updates as soon
OL,15,Fas more information becomes available.
OL,17,F"Southern Water teams continue to work
OL,18,Fclosely with Rother District Council,
OL,19,Fwhich is leading the clean-up efforts,
OL,20,Fand we remain committed to supporting
OL,21,Fthis work in every way we can.
