OL,4,Cof worst pollution spills' at Camber
OL,5,CSands
OL,7,F"Southern Water volunteers will
OL,8,Fcontinue to assist. Our staff are
OL,9,Fthere to help, and we ask that they
OL,10,Fare treated with respect as they help
OL,11,Fwith the beach clean."
OL,13,FThe MP for Hastings and Rye, Helen
OL,14,FDollimore, said she would be putting
OL,15,Fpressure on Southern Water to explain
OL,16,Fhow the biobeads got into the marine
OL,17,Fsystem.
