OL,5,CSands
OL,7,FStrandliners, a not-for-profit
OL,8,Forganisation which monitors pollution
OL,9,Falong the south coast, has been
OL,10,Fworking alongside the Environment
OL,11,FAgency and the council to clear up the
OL,12,Fspillage as best they can.
OL,14,FThe charity said: "This is the worst
OL,15,Fplastic pellet pollution incident we
OL,16,Fhave ever seen here. "
