OL,3,CSouthern Water apologises after 'one
OL,4,Cof worst pollution spills' at Camber
OL,5,CSands
OL,7,F"The impact on the environment and
OL,8,Flocal wildlife can be catastrophic.
OL,9,FBirds and marine animals easily
OL,10,Fmistake these toxic plastic pellets
OL,11,Ffor food.
OL,13,F"Once ingested, it is difficult from
OL,14,Fthem to expel the pellets, and they
OL,15,Fmay either die of starvation or from
OL,16,Fthe cumulative effects of the toxins
OL,17,Fthey contain."
